    "data": [
        {
            "title": "倍耐力的中國投資者提出方案以解決潛在的美國監管擔憂",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:倍耐力;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/倍耐力\">倍耐力</a>最大的投資者中國中化集團已提交一份提案，旨在解決這家義大利輪胎製造商的治理問題及潛在的美國監管擔憂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中化集團旗下持有倍耐力約34%股份的中國化工橡膠周一在聲明中表示，該計畫依托「標準的企業工具和國際最佳實踐，旨在解決治理安排以及任何與美國法規相關的問題」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該集團表示其支持進行中立、基於事實的審查，並準備與相關各方進行誠意對話。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這家中國企業提出上述方案之際，圍繞倍耐力的僵局進一步擴大。在義大利監管機構動用所謂的黃金權力規定施壓後，倍耐力董事會去年宣布終止中化的控股地位。中化對此提出異議，聲稱其仍是倍耐力的第一大股東。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-88c55790-3753-383f-9837-71dd8dcbb7d0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著美國對中國參與聯網汽車領域的審查日益嚴格，這一爭端變得愈發緊迫。倍耐力逾20%的營收來自美國市場，其高管曾警告稱，隨著華盛頓收緊對華相關技術的限制，若治理問題懸而未決，公司對美市場的准入可能受到威脅。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：倍耐力股東Camfin將不再與中化集團續簽股東協議</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Pirelli’s Chinese Investor Proposes Plan to Address US Concerns</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%80%8D%E8%80%90%E5%8A%9B%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%80%85%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E4%BB%A5%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA%E6%BD%9B%E5%9C%A8%E7%9A%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%9B%A3%E7%AE%A1%E6%93%94%E6%86%82-182022301.html",
