        {
            "title": "微軟發布最新人工智能晶片 旨在減少對輝達依賴",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 微軟公司推出第二代人工智能晶片，旨在提高服務產品性能並減少對輝達晶片的依賴。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這款名為Maia 200的晶片由台積電生產，目前正陸續運往微軟位於愛荷華州的數據中心，下一站將部署在鳳凰城地區。微軟於周一邀請開發者開始使用Maia的控制軟件，目前尚不清楚Azure雲服務的用戶何時能使用搭載該晶片的伺服器。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">微軟雲計算與人工智能主管Scott Guthrie在博客文章中表示，首批晶片中的一部分將交付給微軟的超級人工智能團隊，用於生成數據以改進下一代AI模型。這些晶片還將用於驅動面向企業的Copilot助手，以及微軟租賃給雲客戶的AI模型（包括 OpenAI的最新模型）。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5acc7351-de52-38e6-97e9-e5e677562c74-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">微軟表示，其晶片在某些AI任務上的性能優於谷歌和亞馬遜雲服務的同類半導體。「Maia 200也是微軟部署過的最高效的推理系統，」Guthrie說道。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司表示，目前已在設計下一代晶片Maia 300。如果內部研發受挫，微軟還有其他選擇：作為與OpenAI協議的一部分，微軟有權使用這家ChatGPT製造商初期的晶片設計方案。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Microsoft Unveils Latest AI Chip to Reduce Reliance on Nvidia</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BE%AE%E8%BB%9F%E7%99%BC%E5%B8%83%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87-%E6%97%A8%E5%9C%A8%E6%B8%9B%E5%B0%91%E5%B0%8D%E8%BC%9D%E9%81%94%E4%BE%9D%E8%B3%B4-164742648.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-27 01:38:05",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "英國AI搶飯碗最嚴重",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博引述摩根士丹利最新研究指出，英國因人工智能（AI）導致的就業流失已超過其所創造新增職位，且流失速度明顯快過其他主要經濟體，對本地勞動市場構成額外壓力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>大摩：一年淨流失8%職位</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報告顯示，過去12個月，英國就業職位因AI出現而淨減少約8%，是國際平均水平的兩倍，在美國、德國、日本及澳洲等受調查國家中居首。研究涵蓋至少使用AI一年以上的企業，涉及消費必需品與零售、房地產、交通運輸、醫療設備及汽車等行業。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-ed284ba5-94a3-3e2d-8dc2-dc2b3c08fa4c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">結果顯示，英國企業受惠AI平均錄得11.5%的生產力提升，其中近半數企業增幅更高，反映技術投資已開始產生實際回報。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">大摩表示，英國僱主更傾向削減需要2至5年工作經驗的初級職位，使年輕勞動力面臨更大衝擊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博分析英國國家統計局網上職位空缺數據稱，雖然各行業招聘職位普遍減少，但英國企業正以明顯更快的速度縮減那些可能受到AI影響的職位，包括軟件開發人員和諮詢顧問。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8Bai%E6%90%B6%E9%A3%AF%E7%A2%97%E6%9C%80%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D-175300492.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-27 01:58:15",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "貝萊德稱2025年歐洲股票ETF吸引資金規模相當於此前十年",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"642\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/uMuX6ElACOpUJzs8pI47oA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/9a9060096bd46440f15e4f2e0f80ce90\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 貝萊德的Ursula Marchioni表示，2025年市場對專注於歐洲股票的交易所交易(ETF)產品的需求非常強勁，一年內吸引了相當於十年的資金流入。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">身為全球最大資產管理公司EMEA投資和投資組合解決方案主管的Marchioni在接受彭博電視採訪時表示，這些基金去年吸引了920億美元的資金，接近2014年至2024年間累計獲得的940億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">資金流動凸顯出投資者對歐洲股票日益成長的需求，他們正在尋求美國以外的投資機會。在美國，創紀錄的漲勢主要由少數受益於人工智能繁榮的股票推動。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f1937c0f-6432-3ac9-b594-9a2fd1bf34b5-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Marchioni說：「去年我們看到了大規模的交易回流。人們希望分散投資，繼續參與人工智能貿易和美國市場，但同時又希望獲得某種形式的保護。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"觀看視頻：貝萊德的Ursula Marchioni接受彭博電視採訪來源： 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ubjf0Lv1npBnJsUB4WibKQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/ba2a052f238afa78b7ed2cd24f43420c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">觀看視頻：貝萊德的Ursula Marchioni接受彭博電視採訪來源： 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">鑒於德國等政府加大支出，人們對歐洲經濟前景持樂觀態度。彭博行業研究匯編的數據顯示，分析師預計今年斯托克600指數的利潤將成長約10%，而之前2025年的成長為零。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Marchioni表示，「我們相信會實現非常強勁的盈利。我認為投資者會希望參與其中，但同時也會考慮其他多元化投資因素，例如投資人工智能相關或更廣泛的領域，比如歐洲國防或美國醫療健保。」</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"642\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/YJM0Yq6E0IEVsOn6bus6eA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/b5a316ba7f7eca4d7c59598b00c97a14\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以美元計價的歐洲股市自去年初以來已上漲37%，是同期標普500指數漲幅的兩倍。近期，歐洲股市的漲勢遍及各個板塊，其中銀行、礦業和國防板塊均表現優異。此外，歐洲股市的估值也比美國股市更為合理，這也吸引了眾多投資者。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題BlackRock Says Europe Draws a ‘Decade in a Year’ of Stock Flows</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%9D%E8%90%8A%E5%BE%B7%E7%A8%B12025%E5%B9%B4%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%A8etf%E5%90%B8%E5%BC%95%E8%B3%87%E9%87%91%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E7%9B%B8%E7%95%B6%E6%96%BC%E6%AD%A4%E5%89%8D%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4-152746287.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-27 01:13:07",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國耐久財訂單創六個月來最大增幅",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國11月耐久財訂單增幅創六個月來最大，得益於商用飛機及其他資本設備訂單的推動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國商務部報告顯示，耐久財（指使用壽命至少三年的商品）訂單成長5.3%，前月數據經修正後為下降2.1%。該報告因聯邦政府停擺而推遲發布。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周一公佈的數據顯示，核心資本貨物訂單（即不包含飛機和軍事裝備的設備投資指標）成長0.7%，增幅超出預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Durable Goods Orders Increase by Most in Six Months</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c52c5287-e987-3a4f-acd0-9d8c460e0147-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Chris Middleton.</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%80%90%E4%B9%85%E8%B2%A1%E8%A8%82%E5%96%AE%E5%89%B5%E5%85%AD%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E5%A2%9E%E5%B9%85-135417179.html",
